name: Lush Life
comments: Vocal plus recitation version. The same volume recorded between 1981 and 1984 includes piano and baritone saxophone instrumental versions. Volume 2 includes three vocal versions - one with Scott accompanying himself on piano, a second set to new music by Bill Frisell , and a third sung by Scott's daughter, Monica Shaka when she was just eleven years old. It also includes two instrumental versions - the first on electric piano and tenor saxophone, and the second on clarinet.
